<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">

    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com/" crossorigin="">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/assets/bootstrap.min.css" />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="https://suustore.com/assets/frontend/images/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/assets/app.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">



    <script>
        window.SuuTruyen = {
            baseUrl: 'https://suustore.com',
            urlCurrent: 'https://suustore.com',
            csrfToken: '4EebYu2rWivdRk1ET12dyuY0CJjpRERhJynPtvUy'
        }
    </script>

    <title>Demo Truyện</title>
    <meta name="description"
          content="Đọc truyện online, truyện hay. Demo Truyện luôn tổng hợp và cập nhật các chương truyện một cách nhanh nhất.">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header d-none d-lg-block">
        <!-- place navbar here -->
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark header__navbar p-md-0">
            <div class="container">
                <a class="navbar-brand" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">
                    <img src="~/assets/images/logo_text.png" alt="Logo Suu Truyen" srcset="" class="img-fluid"
                         style="width: 200px;">
                </a>
                <div class="form-check form-switch me-3 d-flex align-items-center">
                    <label class="form-check-label">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="25" height="25" fill="currentColor"
                             class="bi bi-brightness-high" viewBox="0 0 16 16" style="fill: #fff;">
                            <path d="M8 11a3 3 0 1 1 0-6 3 3 0 0 1 0 6zm0 1a4 4 0 1 0 0-8 4 4 0 0 0 0 8zM8 0a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v2a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-2A.5.5 0 0 1 8 0zm0 13a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5v2a.5.5 0 0 1-1 0v-2A.5.5 0 0 1 8 13zm8-5a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5h-2a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h2a.5.5 0 0 1 .5.5zM3 8a.5.5 0 0 1-.5.5h-2a.5.5 0 0 1 0-1h2A.5.5 0 0 1 3 8zm10.657-5.657a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .707l-1.414 1.415a.5.5 0 1 1-.707-.708l1.414-1.414a.5.5 0 0 1 .707 0zm-9.193 9.193a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .707L3.05 13.657a.5.5 0 0 1-.707-.707l1.414-1.414a.5.5 0 0 1 .707 0zm9.193 2.121a.5.5 0 0 1-.707 0l-1.414-1.414a.5.5 0 0 1 .707-.707l1.414 1.414a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .707zM4.464 4.465a.5.5 0 0 1-.707 0L2.343 3.05a.5.5 0 1 1 .707-.707l1.414 1.414a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708z">
                            </path>
                        </svg>
                    </label>
                    <input class="form-check-input theme_mode" type="checkbox"
                           style="transform: scale(1.3); margin-left: 12px; margin-right: 12px;">

                    <label class="form-check-label">
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="25" height="25" viewBox="0 0 384 512"
                             style="fill: #fff;">
                            <path d="M144.7 98.7c-21 34.1-33.1 74.3-33.1 117.3c0 98 62.8 181.4 150.4 211.7c-12.4 2.8-25.3 4.3-38.6 4.3C126.6 432 48 353.3 48 256c0-68.9 39.4-128.4 96.8-157.3zm62.1-66C91.1 41.2 0 137.9 0 256C0 379.7 100 480 223.5 480c47.8 0 92-15 128.4-40.6c1.9-1.3 3.7-2.7 5.5-4c4.8-3.6 9.4-7.4 13.9-11.4c2.7-2.4 5.3-4.8 7.9-7.3c5-4.9 6.3-12.5 3.1-18.7s-10.1-9.7-17-8.5c-3.7 .6-7.4 1.2-11.1 1.6c-5 .5-10.1 .9-15.3 1c-1.2 0-2.5 0-3.7 0c-.1 0-.2 0-.3 0c-96.8-.2-175.2-78.9-175.2-176c0-54.8 24.9-103.7 64.1-136c1-.9 2.1-1.7 3.2-2.6c4-3.2 8.2-6.2 12.5-9c3.1-2 6.3-4 9.6-5.8c6.1-3.5 9.2-10.5 7.7-17.3s-7.3-11.9-14.3-12.5c-3.6-.3-7.1-.5-10.7-.6c-2.7-.1-5.5-.1-8.2-.1c-3.3 0-6.5 .1-9.8 .2c-2.3 .1-4.6 .2-6.9 .4z">
                            </path>
                        </svg>
                    </label>
                </div>

                <div class="user-section ms-3 d-flex align-items-center">
                    @if (User.Identity?.IsAuthenticated == true)
                    {
                        <div class="dropdown">
                            <a class="d-flex align-items-center dropdown-toggle" role="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown"
                               aria-expanded="false" style="text-decoration: none;">
                                <img src="https://static.vecteezy.com/system/resources/previews/024/183/525/non_2x/avatar-of-a-man-portrait-of-a-young-guy-illustration-of-male-character-in-modern-color-style-vector.jpg"
                            alt="Avatar"
                            class="rounded-circle me-2"
                            style="width: 40px; height: 40px; object-fit: cover;">
                                <span class="text-white">@User.Identity.Name</span>
                            </a>
                            <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="User" asp-action="Profile">Thông tin cá nhân</a></li>
                                <li><a class="dropdown-item" asp-controller="User" asp-action="Logout">Đăng xuất</a></li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    }
                    else
                    {
                        <a asp-controller="User" asp-action="Login" class="btn btn-outline-light">Đăng nhập</a>
                    }
                </div>
            </div>

        </nav>

    </header>

    <div class="bg-light header-bottom">
        <div class="container py-1">
            <p class="mb-0">
                Đọc truyện online, đọc truyện chữ, truyện full, truyện hay. Tổng hợp đầy đủ và cập nhật liên
                tục.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Nút Chat Bot -->
    <div class="chatbot-btn" id="chatBotButton">
        <span class="chat-prompt">Click để hỏi chuyện</span>
        <button class="btn" id="chatBotToggle">
            <i class="bi bi-chat-dots"></i>
        </button>
    </div>

    <!-- Chat Box -->
    <div class="chat-box" id="chatBox">
        <div class="chat-header">
            <span>Chat Bot</span>
            <button class="close-chat-btn" id="closeChat">×</button>
        </div>
        <div class="chat-body">
            <!-- Tin nhắn sẽ hiển thị ở đây -->
        </div>
        <div class="chat-footer">
            <input type="text" id="chatInput" class="form-control" placeholder="Gửi tin nhắn...">
            <button id="sendMessage" class="btn btn-primary">Gửi</button>
        </div>

    </div>


    <div class="container">
        <main role="main" >
            @RenderBody()
        </main>
    </div>


    <div id="footer" class="footer border-top pt-4 bg-dark text-light">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <!-- Logo và mô tả -->
                <div class="col-md-6 text-center text-md-start mb-3 mb-md-0">
                    <h5 class="fw-bold">Suu Truyện</h5>
                    <p class="mb-1">
                        <a title="Đọc truyện online" class="text-light text-decoration-none" href="#">Đọc truyện</a> online nhanh chóng, hỗ trợ mọi thiết bị.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Giấy phép -->
                <div class="col-md-6 text-center text-md-end">
                    <a rel="license" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/">
                        <img alt="Creative Commons License" class="img-fluid mb-2"
                             src="~/assets/images/88x31.png" style="width: 100px;">
                    </a>
                    <p class="mb-0">
                        Website hoạt động theo
                        <a rel="license" class="text-light text-decoration-underline"
                           href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/">
                            Creative Commons Attribution 4.0
                        </a>.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Footer nhỏ bên dưới -->
            <div class="row border-top mt-4 pt-3">
                <div class="col-12 text-center">
                    <small>&copy; 2024 Suu Truyện. Tất cả quyền được bảo lưu.</small>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="~/assets/jquery.min.js">
    </script>
    <script src="~/assets/popper.min.js">
    </script>
    <script src="~/assets/bootstrap.min.js">
    </script>
    <script src="~/assets/app.js">
    </script>
    <script src="~/assets/common.js"></script>



    <div id="loadingPage" class="loading-full">
        <div class="loading-full_icon">
            <div class="spinner-grow"><span class="visually-hidden">Loading...</span></div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>